      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/wheat-hits-two-month-high-after-ukraine-says-russia-strikes-ship</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰称俄罗斯用导弹击中一艘粮食运输船后，小麦期货一度上涨 2.2%。]]></description>
